flowchart LR
  U[User Request] --> P[Planner (LLM / Untrusted)]
  P -->|proposed plan + actions| E[Executor (Deterministic)]
  E -->|validate vs schema
  allow-list & authZ| V{Valid?}
  V -- No --> R[Repair Prompt
  (ask LLM to fix)] --> P
  V -- Yes --> T[Tool Adapter] --> S[(Services/APIs)]
  S --> T --> E
  E -->|structured result| P --> O[Final Answer]
